quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  99,1,"'idha rujjat al'ard rjjana shdydana, wa'akhrajat ma fi btnha min mwta wknwz, watasa'al al'iinsan fzeana: ma aldhy hadath lha?"
  99,2,"'idha rujjat al'ard rjjana shdydana, wa'akhrajat ma fi btnha min mwta wknwz, watasa'al al'iinsan fzeana: ma aldhy hadath lha?"
  99,3,"'idha rujjat al'ard rjjana shdydana, wa'akhrajat ma fi btnha min mwta wknwz, watasa'al al'iinsan fzeana: ma aldhy hadath lha?"
  99,4,"ywm alqiamat tukhbir al'ard bima euml ealayha min khayr 'aw shr, wabi'an allah subhanah wteala 'amriha bi'ana tukhbir bima euml elyha"
  99,5,"ywm alqiamat tukhbir al'ard bima euml ealayha min khayr 'aw shr, wabi'an allah subhanah wteala 'amriha bi'ana tukhbir bima euml elyha"
  99,6,"ywmydh yarjie alnaas ean mawqif alhisab asnafana mtfrqyn; lyryhm allah ma eamiluu min alsayiyaat walhsnat, wyjazyhm elyha"
  99,7,"fmn yaemal wazn namlat saghirat khyrana, yar thwabh fi alakhrt, waman yaemal wazn namlat saghirat shrana, yar eqabh fi alakhrt"
  99,8,"fmn yaemal wazn namlat saghirat khyrana, yar thwabh fi alakhrt, waman yaemal wazn namlat saghirat shrana, yar eqabh fi alakhrt"